item.title: Are Corgis easy to raise? What do you know about the personality traits of a Corgi?
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: Are Corgis easy to raise? What do you know about the personality traits of a Corgi? Time：2018-06-07 19:36 Source：Today’s headlines Editor-in-charge：FoDuo **The first thing I noticed is that there are a lot of different ways to get rid of a corgi. What do you know about the personality traits of a Corgi? Corgis are small, like a quiet environment, and never bark, making them perfect for families. So is a Corgi easy to keep?
